title: Apartment for rent
description:
Steps from the Civic Theatre, Memorial Hospital, and all downtown has to offer. 5-minute drive to Notre Dame (1.7 miles).

Beautiful and historic 1-bedroom apartment located in the Chapin Park Historic district.

*9 ft ceilings
*Ample storage 
*Direct access to a large, shared, fenced back yard
*Hardwood Floors
*Decorative Fireplace
*Dishwasher
*Shared Washer Dryer
*Fully Furnished
